  "description": "Replication package for the paper 'Grounding Doesn't Pay: A Token-Matched Negative Result on Creative Diversity' — a pre-registered, judge-free, token-matched pilot showing in-context domain grounding is never the token-efficient frontier for creative diversity. Includes the frozen generation, the pre-registered scorer, encoder-robustness re-scores, and a Merkle-tree + hash-chain provenance seal.",
